model_diag <- function(actual, pred) {
  MSE = mse(actual,pred)
  RMSE = rmse(actual,pred)
  print(paste0('Mean squared error =',MSE,' , ', 'Root mean sq error =', RMSE))
}
test$pred4 <- predict(fit4, newdata = test )
model_diag(train$medv,fit4$fitted.values)
